[
  {
    "text": "Rock",
    "start": 12.4,
    "duration": 4.83
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 14.04,
    "duration": 3.19
  },
  {
    "text": "nothing.",
    "start": 20.64,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Wow.",
    "start": 33.68,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 36.83,
    "duration": 5.09
  },
  {
    "text": "Why? Why are you doing this? Why have",
    "start": 38.32,
    "duration": 7.399
  },
  {
    "text": "you betrayed me?",
    "start": 41.92,
    "duration": 3.799
  },
  {
    "text": "A",
    "start": 52.719,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "look.",
    "start": 64.239,
    "duration": 4.721
  },
  {
    "text": "What's that?",
    "start": 67.04,
    "duration": 5.88
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Those are deer monsters.",
    "start": 68.96,
    "duration": 3.96
  },
  {
    "text": "He's",
    "start": 73.28,
    "duration": 5.08
  },
  {
    "text": "He's gone.",
    "start": 75.04,
    "duration": 3.32
  },
  {
    "text": "The cultists. They did this. We have to",
    "start": 83.439,
    "duration": 4.801
  },
  {
    "text": "go after them.",
    "start": 86.64,
    "duration": 6.72
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Wait, Dino, kid, where's your hat? You",
    "start": 88.24,
    "duration": 7.6
  },
  {
    "text": "never take it off.",
    "start": 93.36,
    "duration": 6.32
  },
  {
    "text": ">> I I can't remember.",
    "start": 95.84,
    "duration": 5.68
  },
  {
    "text": ">> It doesn't matter right now. We need to",
    "start": 99.68,
    "duration": 6.16
  },
  {
    "text": "get to their base. Come on.",
    "start": 101.52,
    "duration": 6.559
  },
  {
    "text": ">> All right, you stupid cultist. Show",
    "start": 105.84,
    "duration": 4.959
  },
  {
    "text": "yourself.",
    "start": 108.079,
    "duration": 2.72
  },
  {
    "text": "Where is everyone? This place is usually",
    "start": 111.52,
    "duration": 5.04
  },
  {
    "text": "crawling with those guys. They must have",
    "start": 114.159,
    "duration": 6.401
  },
  {
    "text": "fled. Look for evidence.",
    "start": 116.56,
    "duration": 7.0
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Huh?",
    "start": 120.56,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Hey, what's this?",
    "start": 131.2,
    "duration": 3.92
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Not now, Koala Kid. We're looking for",
    "start": 133.04,
    "duration": 6.0
  },
  {
    "text": "proof, not pretty crystals. Focus.",
    "start": 135.12,
    "duration": 6.479
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey, I found something.",
    "start": 139.04,
    "duration": 5.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Upon the dawn of the full moon, we shall",
    "start": 141.599,
    "duration": 4.801
  },
  {
    "text": "commence our journey to the far away",
    "start": 144.16,
    "duration": 4.159
  },
  {
    "text": "lands.",
    "start": 146.4,
    "duration": 4.02
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Huh?",
    "start": 148.319,
    "duration": 3.841
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 150.42,
    "duration": 3.58
  },
  {
    "text": "Do it. Do it. Do it.",
    "start": 152.16,
    "duration": 5.96
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Stay back. I got this.",
    "start": 154.0,
    "duration": 4.12
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Wait. Don't you remember what the dear",
    "start": 160.0,
    "duration": 6.16
  },
  {
    "text": "monster taught us? We should be nice to",
    "start": 162.879,
    "duration": 7.321
  },
  {
    "text": "all the forest animals.",
    "start": 166.16,
    "duration": 4.04
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 174.96,
    "duration": 3.879
  },
  {
    "text": "He says he's sorry for scaring us. He",
    "start": 179.28,
    "duration": 4.64
  },
  {
    "text": "doesn't mean any harm.",
    "start": 182.159,
    "duration": 3.681
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Wait a minute. You can talk to that",
    "start": 183.92,
    "duration": 2.399
  },
  {
    "text": "thing.",
    "start": 185.84,
    "duration": 4.84
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Ask if it saw the cultist yesterday.",
    "start": 186.319,
    "duration": 4.361
  },
  {
    "text": "He says they all left early in the day,",
    "start": 196.4,
    "duration": 4.64
  },
  {
    "text": "way before the moon was out. Their",
    "start": 198.879,
    "duration": 5.28
  },
  {
    "text": "leader said something about the red",
    "start": 201.04,
    "duration": 5.22
  },
  {
    "text": "reptiles cleansing.",
    "start": 204.159,
    "duration": 3.841
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 206.26,
    "duration": 4.86
  },
  {
    "text": ">> But dear monster was killed last night.",
    "start": 208.0,
    "duration": 5.28
  },
  {
    "text": "If they already left for some ritual,",
    "start": 211.12,
    "duration": 4.399
  },
  {
    "text": "the cultists couldn't have done it.",
    "start": 213.28,
    "duration": 4.879
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Then who did?",
    "start": 215.519,
    "duration": 4.72
  },
  {
    "text": ">> We must have missed something earlier.",
    "start": 218.159,
    "duration": 6.041
  },
  {
    "text": "Look around for more clues.",
    "start": 220.239,
    "duration": 3.961
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Ah, Dino, what's your missing hat doing",
    "start": 225.76,
    "duration": 6.36
  },
  {
    "text": "at the scene of the crime?",
    "start": 228.239,
    "duration": 3.881
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 234.86,
    "duration": 6.9
  },
  {
    "text": "Uh, I don't know.",
    "start": 238.319,
    "duration": 6.161
  },
  {
    "text": ">> You don't know? It's literally your hat",
    "start": 241.76,
    "duration": 4.399
  },
  {
    "text": "right next to where Deer Monster was",
    "start": 244.48,
    "duration": 2.88
  },
  {
    "text": "murdered.",
    "start": 246.159,
    "duration": 3.921
  },
  {
    "text": ">> I told you I don't remember.",
    "start": 247.36,
    "duration": 6.159
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay, calm down everyone. I'm sure",
    "start": 250.08,
    "duration": 5.999
  },
  {
    "text": "that's just a coincidence. Let's keep",
    "start": 253.519,
    "duration": 5.56
  },
  {
    "text": "looking.",
    "start": 256.079,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": ">> You might have them fooled, Dino, but",
    "start": 259.6,
    "duration": 3.76
  },
  {
    "text": "not me.",
    "start": 262.4,
    "duration": 3.6
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Check it out. Footprints,",
    "start": 263.36,
    "duration": 7.32
  },
  {
    "text": "tear monsters, and some humans.",
    "start": 266.0,
    "duration": 4.68
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Too bad we'll never be able to figure",
    "start": 271.44,
    "duration": 2.88
  },
  {
    "text": "out who's.",
    "start": 273.28,
    "duration": 4.52
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Oh, yeah.",
    "start": 274.32,
    "duration": 3.48
  },
  {
    "text": "Dino,",
    "start": 278.639,
    "duration": 4.0
  },
  {
    "text": ">> don't lie. That's your shoe. It's an",
    "start": 280.24,
    "duration": 3.679
  },
  {
    "text": "exact match.",
    "start": 282.639,
    "duration": 5.721
  },
  {
    "text": ">> No, it could be.",
    "start": 283.919,
    "duration": 4.441
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Just tell us the truth. We all make",
    "start": 290.08,
    "duration": 4.64
  },
  {
    "text": "mistakes, but we can forgive you.",
    "start": 292.32,
    "duration": 6.56
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Forgive him. He murdered our friend.",
    "start": 294.72,
    "duration": 8.16
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Stop it. Dino's our brother. He never",
    "start": 298.88,
    "duration": 8.72
  },
  {
    "text": "hurt anyone, especially dear monster.",
    "start": 302.88,
    "duration": 6.72
  },
  {
    "text": "You're right. Let's see where these",
    "start": 307.6,
    "duration": 3.84
  },
  {
    "text": "tracks lead.",
    "start": 309.6,
    "duration": 4.4
  },
  {
    "text": ">> See, I told you they go right to Dino",
    "start": 311.44,
    "duration": 5.039
  },
  {
    "text": "Kid's tent. What more proof do you need?",
    "start": 314.0,
    "duration": 5.039
  },
  {
    "text": ">> How could you do this? Deer Monster was",
    "start": 316.479,
    "duration": 5.56
  },
  {
    "text": "family.",
    "start": 319.039,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": ">> No, it's not true.",
    "start": 329.759,
    "duration": 8.16
  },
  {
    "text": ">> No. Where are you taking him?",
    "start": 334.16,
    "duration": 5.28
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Back to the volcano.",
    "start": 337.919,
    "duration": 5.401
  },
  {
    "text": ">> We're going to make him confess.",
    "start": 339.44,
    "duration": 3.88
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Ain't no D is innocent. He has to be",
    "start": 343.36,
    "duration": 7.279
  },
  {
    "text": "evil. I just need to find something to",
    "start": 347.36,
    "duration": 6.52
  },
  {
    "text": "prove it.",
    "start": 350.639,
    "duration": 3.241
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 358.09,
    "duration": 3.16
  },
  {
    "text": "What are you doing here? Leave him",
    "start": 385.12,
    "duration": 4.96
  },
  {
    "text": "alone.",
    "start": 387.52,
    "duration": 7.84
  },
  {
    "text": "H Why did they run off so easily?",
    "start": 390.08,
    "duration": 8.32
  },
  {
    "text": "Go back to sleep, little one. I scared",
    "start": 395.36,
    "duration": 6.64
  },
  {
    "text": "them away. Dino kid, what are you?",
    "start": 398.4,
    "duration": 5.919
  },
  {
    "text": ">> The cultists, they use this crystal to",
    "start": 402.0,
    "duration": 5.28
  },
  {
    "text": "prank Dino. I have to save him.",
    "start": 404.319,
    "duration": 5.361
  },
  {
    "text": ">> No, please. I don't know what you want",
    "start": 407.28,
    "duration": 4.639
  },
  {
    "text": "me to say. I didn't do it.",
    "start": 409.68,
    "duration": 5.04
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Don't lie to us. We saw the evidence.",
    "start": 411.919,
    "duration": 7.201
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Come clean before it's too late. Wait.",
    "start": 414.72,
    "duration": 6.96
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't do it.",
    "start": 419.12,
    "duration": 6.96
  },
  {
    "text": "He's innocent. The cultists framed him.",
    "start": 421.68,
    "duration": 7.519
  },
  {
    "text": "They used a crystal to brainwash him.",
    "start": 426.08,
    "duration": 5.679
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Huh? That's the crystal from the book.",
    "start": 429.199,
    "duration": 4.56
  },
  {
    "text": ">> We fell right into their trap.",
    "start": 431.759,
    "duration": 6.121
  },
  {
    "text": ">> They're going to pay for this.",
    "start": 433.759,
    "duration": 4.121
  },
  {
    "text": ">> What? I I remember now. I remember",
    "start": 438.24,
    "duration": 7.359
  },
  {
    "text": "everything. I'm so sorry. I couldn't",
    "start": 442.24,
    "duration": 4.239
  },
  {
    "text": "control it.",
    "start": 445.599,
    "duration": 6.681
  },
  {
    "text": ">> It's okay. It wasn't you. It was them.",
    "start": 446.479,
    "duration": 5.801
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Wait a minute. Only one of these symbols",
    "start": 453.759,
    "duration": 3.201
  },
  {
    "text": "is lit.",
    "start": 456.08,
    "duration": 1.6
  },
  {
    "text": ">> So,",
    "start": 456.96,
    "duration": 2.72
  },
  {
    "text": ">> well, that means the crystal you just",
    "start": 457.68,
    "duration": 4.639
  },
  {
    "text": "destroyed was the only sacrifice made.",
    "start": 459.68,
    "duration": 4.48
  },
  {
    "text": ">> But if that's true, then",
    "start": 462.319,
    "duration": 5.88
  },
  {
    "text": ">> the monster's alive.",
    "start": 464.16,
    "duration": 4.039
  },
  {
    "text": "There monster.",
    "start": 479.919,
    "duration": 3.321
  }
]